recommend keep-going -- three real laps landed and proven GREEN in one sitting now that the cloud toolchain is raised. The deterministic-simulation horizon (seeded fault/delay injection over the replica set) remains the one item this pass deliberately deferred, per Keaton's own earlier framing that it deserves its own dedicated pass rather than being folded into a mechanical sibling lap.
